        jLabel5.setFont(new java.awt.Font("Segoe UI", 0, 18)); // NOI18N
        jLabel5.setText("<html><body>\n\nNestled within the serene landscapes of Cox's Bazar, Shoilo Propat, or the Shoilo Waterfall, is a natural jewel that captivates visitors with its tranquil beauty. As one ventures<br>\nthrough the lush greenery of Himchari National Park, the rhythmic sound of cascading water heralds the approach to this enchanting waterfall. Shoilo Propat descendsgracefully<br>\namidst verdant foliage, creating a picturesque scene that invites travelers to pause and immerse themselves in nature's embrace. The surrounding area, rich in biodiversity, enhances<br>\nthe allure of the waterfall, providing a peaceful escape for those seeking solace in the heart of Cox's Bazar. Shoilo Propat stands as a testament to the region's natural splendor, offering<br> a serene haven where visitors can connect with the beauty of Bangladesh's landscapes.\n\n</body></html>");
        jPanel1.add(jLabel5, new org.netbeans.lib.awtextra.AbsoluteConstraints(0, 770, 950, 240));

